#Librairies n√©cessaires: SDL, SDL_image, python-dev

install and setup instruction for SDL on linux (apt-get package manager) :

apt-get :
$ sudo apt-get install libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-mixer1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev

install and setup for python on linux (apt-get package manager) :

$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install python3.4-dev

To compile, simply use the cmake ( Using QtCreator is better! )
